---
title: Lemony Spaghetti with Chicken & Brussels sprinkled with Toasted Panko & Scallions
description: Does your love for pasta know no bounds? We’ve got the perfect recipe for any self-professed carb connoisseur. Al dente spaghetti, shredded Brussels sprouts, Parmesan, and lemon come together in a combination that’s hearty, satisfying, and classically comforting. Just add a sprinkle of chili flakes and crunchy toasted panko over the top to take things, well... over the top!
